ðŸ”„ Quick Recap of Tools:
| Tool      | What it lists / switches                                     |
| --------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| `kubectx` | Shows and switches **contexts** (clusters/configs)           |
| `kubens`  | Shows and switches **namespaces** within the current context |

âœ… To Install kubens (alongside kubectx):
wget https://github.com/ahmetb/kubectx/releases/download/v0.9.5/kubens_v0.9.5_linux_x86_64.tar.gz
tar -xzf kubens_v0.9.5_linux_x86_64.tar.gz
mv kubens /usr/local/bin/
chmod +x /usr/local/bin/kubens

